Package de.oth.blocklib.threading

Class DelegatingCompletableFuture<T>

java.lang.Object
java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<T>
de.oth.blocklib.threading.DelegatingCompletableFuture<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.concurrent.CompletionStage<T>, java.util.concurrent.Future<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
DelegatingScheduledCompletableFuture
class DelegatingCompletableFuture<T>
extends java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<T>
implements java.util.concurrent.Future<T>
Delegates cancel and complete calls to an inner Future. Async CompletableFuture composition uses a statically initialized BlocklibExecutorService instead of ForkJoinPool.commonPool().
Author:
Loher Florian
